{"tid":104730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［共享］馬鞍山綫全新支那列車試行！","createTime":"2017-02-02T10:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T16:16:32.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"938953da0420eecba15a49bf0f63bec41df0c9b2","tid":104730,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"【馬鞍山綫全新列車試行！】<br />\n馬鞍山綫首兩列八卡列車已經喺上個月中投入服務，唔知大家搭過未呢？而馬鞍山綫第一列全新八卡車(即係沿綫第三列八卡車)亦都做緊一系列嚴謹嘅測試，準備以最fit嘅狀態同各位見面！ <br />\n<br />\n呢款新八卡車嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">系統同設備係嚟自日本、德國、英國同法國等地，集齊之後喺內地進行組裝。而車廂內籠就係由法國公司設計，</span></span>希望令乘客旅程更舒適。#全新馬鞍山綫八卡車做緊測試喇 #嶄新車廂設計更舒適<br />\n<br />\n[New 8-car train in trial runs on the Ma On Shan Line]<br />\nYou may aware that the first two Ma On Shan Line 8-car trains have commenced service since mid-January this year. And the third train, which is also the first brand new one, is undergoing a series of stringent tests in preparation for passenger service. <br />\n<br />\nThe <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">systems and facilities for the new 8-car train were procured from Japan, Germany, the United Kingdom and France and the train was assembled in China. The interior was designed by a French-owned company</span></span> and will provide passengers with a more comfortable travelling environment."},{"pid":"1caf196595450fec4e521bd03a148e420ddc613f","tid":104730,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:10:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mtrhk/posts/10158302660390151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmtrhk%2Fposts%2F10158302660390151&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8924d90a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mtrhk/posts/10158302660390151</a>"},{"pid":"f9ae8956975a8c35ae37b2b9610f1ba16a13bdf0","tid":104730,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:16